divs: Sighting Detailsthis was so weird. i was walking my dog. It was late evening. There was a rumblingf sound coming from the sky. It was snowing at the time. There was no stars,just snow clouds. It was like I heard the deep rumbling noise,but I didn't really pay attention to it.Untill,its like weird,I saw lights. Its so hard to explain what they looked like. I know this sounds weird, but, there were just here and gone. Period. Very fast very ah....I don't know,neither here nor there. T
Summary: rumble in the sky large spheres.here and gone
